# Portfolio Website

## 📌 Project Description
This is a personal portfolio website created using HTML and CSS.

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3

## 📂 Features
- Responsive design
- Navigation bar
- About section
- Projects section
- Contact form

## 📱 Responsiveness
The website works on both mobile and desktop screens.

